freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: 5 days after my second vaccine (which was given in my left arm) I was unable to move my left hand or fingers for 25 minutes, but my sensation was intact. I had an MRI, which was normal. I have not experienced these symptoms prior to or since then.
